    # "A frazzled young woman rushes out of the second door on the left, her arms full of papers."
    "Eine gestresste junge Frau eilt aus der zweiten Tür links, die Arme voller Papiere."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:389
translate german tolawoffices_3f829165:

    # "???" "Can I help you? "
    "???" "Kann ich Ihnen helfen? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:390
translate german tolawoffices_81220faf:

    # pc "I'm here about the Help Wanted poster. "
    pc "Ich bin wegen des „HELP WANTED“-Plakats hier. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:391
translate german tolawoffices_59577895:

    # "???" "Oh really? Great! Let me see if Mrs. Mills has time to see you. "
    "???" "Ach wirklich? Super! Ich schaue mal, ob Mrs. Mills Zeit hat, Sie zu empfangen. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:392
translate german tolawoffices_c8235dbf:

    # "???" "Just have a seat over there. "
    "???" "Nehmen Sie doch dort Platz. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:395
